Grey handwoven tussar silk saree

GCSSISLSAA0274

Regular price Rs. 7,500.00 Sale price Rs. 6,000.00 Save 20%
/
Tax included. Shipping calculated at checkout.

Free Shipping

Authentic Products

Quality assured

Please note, All orders on GoCoop Marketplace are processed by our sellers in 24 hours or 1 working day. Domestic orders are delivered in 4-6 working days. International orders from multiple sellers get consolidated in our Bangalore warehouse and will be delivered in 10-14 working days. Thank you.


Product description

feel good in this grey tussar silk handwoven saree from the looms of bihar. the saree has geometric motifs woven in black all over the body. thick and thin black and zari stripes with abstarct motifs are designed on the pallu. the coarseness and the slub effect adds texture to the saree and the sheen enhances its grandeur making it suitable for special occasions.

Product specification :

length : 6.3 m
width : 1.2m (45 inches) material : tussar silk
blouse piece : attached.

Wash care :

dry clean only
* unevenness in weave and slight variations in color is intrinsic to an authentic handmade product

why gocoop?

at gocoop (pronounced go-co-op) we connect India's artisans, weaver co-operatives and clusters directly with consumers across the world. 

our national award winning global platform brings together handloom, handicraft artisans and cooperatives from over 55 clusters, delivering authentic handmade products, ensuring fair prices for both buyer and seller. 

join us in #CraftingChange together.

© 2022 GoCoop

Join us in Crafting Change

Welcome to gocoop, India's first national-award winning online marketplace for weavers and artisans. Subscribe to hear our stories from the clusters, events happening near you and special offers.
